Scenario:  Outlook not responding, error or Outlook freezes when the user open a file or send mail

User story: As a user, I am able to have access to open my email.

Description:  When the user open outlook or send an emai message in outlook in Microsoft, Outlook freezes , or the user receive the following error. "Outlook not responding"


Title: Outlook not responding

Basic flow: 
	1. The user called in saying that he hade a issue with Outlook
	2. I remoted the user computer and I started an automatically repair Office program files to resolve such problems as Outlook freezing or not responding.
	3. The user now need to wait untill the Online repair is done.
	4. I told to him to call in if the the issue persist.
	5. The user agreed to case closure.
